<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.7.5">
<l>eytak kūvuta lāvatē yeṉak kevvatey vattu ḷāyumāy niṉṟu</l>
<l>kaita vaṅkaḷcey yuṅkaru mēṉiyam māṉē</l>
<l>ceyta vēḷviyar vaiyat tēvaraṟāc cirīvara maṅkalanakar</l>
<l>kaittoḻa viruntā yatunāṉuṅ kaṇṭēṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is possible for me to call so that I reach [you], o lord with a black body</l>
<l>who stays as the life in whatever deity [and] did [acts] of cunning.</l>
<l>O you who sit in the city of Cirīvaramaṅkalam while unceasingly the gods on earth,</l>
<l>those with sacrifices they make, worship you with [their] hands [folded], I too have seen that.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
